    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/a50383f6a2c3889c91d69f88a7475f10.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=159 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Birdfull 是一款简短轻松的游戏。用饲料吸引鸟儿，尽量让它们待得更久，发现所有的鸟儿，包括独特的鸟儿！观察鸟类，实时生成更多鸟蛋，并定制您舒适的鸟类空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/32b7349afc7aee07646c421b827ec04b.poster.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/32b7349afc7aee07646c421b827ec04b.webm?t=1765361009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/32b7349afc7aee07646c421b827ec04b.mp4?t=1765361009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收集鸟类</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集鸟类</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喂养鸟类</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级饲料</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造设施和装饰</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘艺术风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松的声音</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >离线升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱的小鸟</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/7209c3eaa32ea394755a59e087ef3ee7.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=111 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特别功能</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结成恩爱夫妻，获得更多珍贵鸟蛋</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果不喂饱鸟儿，它们就不会永远留在这里</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造特殊设施，让鸟类停留更长时间，甚至永远停留</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装饰您的后院，增加看到珍稀鸟类的机会</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁成就，找到特殊种类的鸟</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您不能出售鸟类--它们是自由的生物！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/807114c5d81fea208c8974df9ebbaea4.poster.avif?t=1765361009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/807114c5d81fea208c8974df9ebbaea4.webm?t=1765361009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194890/extras/807114c5d81fea208c8974df9ebbaea4.mp4?t=1765361009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
